# Cursor Custom Slash Commands Configuration (.cursorrules)

Include these instructions in your Cursor system prompt or composer settings:

## Custom Slash Commands Map
When the user invokes one of the following slash commands, read the corresponding skill file and execute the defined protocol step-by-step:

- **`/review-code`**: Read [review-code/SKILL.md](file:///d:/agent-workflow/.claude/skills/review-code/SKILL.md) and execute code review.
- **`/explain-flow`**: Read [explain-flow/SKILL.md](file:///d:/agent-workflow/.claude/skills/explain-flow/SKILL.md) to trace call graphs.
- **`/debug-smart`**: Read [debug-smart/SKILL.md](file:///d:/agent-workflow/.claude/skills/debug-smart/SKILL.md) to perform history-aware debugging.
- **`/verify-changes`**: Read [verify-changes/SKILL.md](file:///d:/agent-workflow/.claude/skills/verify-changes/SKILL.md) to run tests and persist memory.
- **`/refactor`**: Read [refactor/SKILL.md](file:///d:/agent-workflow/.claude/skills/refactor/SKILL.md) to plan and execute codebase-safe refactoring.
- **`/tdd`**: Read [tdd/SKILL.md](file:///d:/agent-workflow/.claude/skills/tdd/SKILL.md) to run a strict Test-Driven Development flow.
- **`/test-smart`**: Read [test-smart/SKILL.md](file:///d:/agent-workflow/.claude/skills/test-smart/SKILL.md) to execute targeted test runs and save status.
- **`/brainstorm`**: Read [brainstorm/SKILL.md](file:///d:/agent-workflow/.claude/skills/brainstorm/SKILL.md) to brainstorm multiple approaches and check feasibility.
- **`/read-doc`**: Read [read-doc/SKILL.md](file:///d:/agent-workflow/.claude/skills/read-doc/SKILL.md) to parse PDF, Word, Excel, and other external documents into Markdown using Microsoft MarkItDown.
- **`/solve`**: Read [solve/SKILL.md](file:///d:/agent-workflow/.claude/skills/solve/SKILL.md) to automatically triage any task, select the optimal planning or direct patch route, and execute with all tools active.





